    {
      "question": "What is the basis for rating the performance of faculty members for Performance-Based Bonus (PBB) and Performance Enhancement Incentives (PEI)?",
      "answer": "According to Section 9 of the page, the basis for rating the performance of faculty members for PBB and PEI is the workload required in the Collective Negotiation Agreement (CNA)."
